abstract: "A physics-informed validation framework for Zero-Noise Extrapolation in NISQ circuits. Introduces a Navier-Stokes energy dissipation filter and Fibonacci noise scaling schedule, evaluated across 17,280 experiment runs covering 3 circuit types, 3 schedules, 3 extrapolants, 8 depths and 8 noise levels."
